{"type": "article", "id": 24686, "title": "Gucci 早秋系列大片出炉，以及，日本这个印花球鞋不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-03-30T10:26:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11440, "name": "睫毛膏"}, {"id": 5684, "name": "早秋系列"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 11718, "name": "印花"}, {"id": 116, "name": "芝加哥"}, {"id": 25173, "name": "新店"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 3134, "name": "Versace"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702160431dbqYcLtnaTxIp36Z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Mercedes-Benz-launches-new-competition-for-young-fashion-designers,675060.html#.Vvsbe4QrJQY\"><b>奔驰为年轻设计师推出新赛事</b></a>｜德国汽车公司 Mercedes-Benz 赞助世界各地的时装周已有 20 年，包括悉尼、墨尔本、纽约、米兰、迈阿密、东京、莫斯科、北京等等，从 2008 年起还与法国时装协会（FFF）合作，最近 Benz 宣布为年轻时装设计师推出新的赛事 'Mercedes-Benz Stars’，Alexis Mabille 担任评审团主席，将由他选出 30 位候选人，6 月 15 日评审团从中选出 10 位晋级选手，终选在 10 月 4 日，巴黎时装周上，最终获奖者将获得 15000 欧元现金奖励和 Benz 的长期支持。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Mercedes-Benz-launches-new-competition-for-young-fashion-designers,675060.html#.Vvsbe4QrJQY\"><b>全球鞋类零售大会即将开幕</b></a>｜全球鞋类零售会议（The Global Footwear Retail Conference ）将于周四即 3 月 31 日在香港会议展览中心开幕，本届将关注国际贸易和跨太平洋合作、千禧一代的时尚消费者、鞋类电商的未来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/american-apparel-board-liz-claiborne-paul-charron-10399931/\"><b>American Apparel 任命新主席</b></a>｜洛杉矶时尚零售品牌 American Apparel 董事会近日宣布新主席将上任，为丽诗加邦 Liz Claiborne 的前主席兼 CEO Paul R. Charron。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/alibaba-jack-ma-zeng-fanzhi-2016-hurun-art-list-10399821/\"><b>马云入选胡润艺术榜</b></a>｜阿里巴巴创始人马云进入各大财富榜单当然不稀奇，最近他还入选了今年的胡润艺术榜，艺术家曾梵志合作的一幅画，在 2015 年香港苏富比秋季拍卖的预览中展出，以 530 万美元拍卖成交后，位列中国在世最贵艺术家作品的第 4 名。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160412tvqOr8eWwN42H5Vk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/designer-luxury/versace-opens-store-chicago-10399219/\"><b>Versace 在芝加哥开新店</b></a>｜意大利时装品牌 Versace 自 2000 年关闭 Oak Street店，16 年后在芝加哥黄金海岸开一家新旗舰店，两层、4951 平方英尺的面积由 Donatella Versace 和英国建筑师 Jamie Fobert 合作设计，延续曼哈顿 SoHo 门店的内部设计风格。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160412gM9Stxyebp2hYmud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160413Dv2XrQUwlS0gcdET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/3/29/11323768/gucci-prefall-2016-campaign\"> Gucci 早秋系列大片</a>，保持了最近一贯的复古、华丽。找来了很多长腿曲颈的火烈鸟入镜：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604131HF2hc4xineJj0lM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160414P7VYBy39AR1Ue8dH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160414DhUWgt1SdoOZV48m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604158RcdWkKY0J61XsoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160415SJ8r6MBRdTNgsOut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">NIGO 要和街头艺术家 KAWS 联手合作的优衣库 UT，最近官方释出了几张新品预告图：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604169o2CgeVHLnz6sPt7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160416iLIAP1zMlCS4sFnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160417gMtDOcbmI2LAd3ZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604170AGsYfnBVtWumLew.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160419NGCf4nybHaL6pIk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160419dmNUo6pOi9x3E05w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">春夏想要更多彩？可以看看日本这个以印花为特色的球鞋品牌 LOSERS，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/3/losers-2016-spring-summer-inside-out-collection\">最新的春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160420CO2LkRq9FdES1e83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160421wV9ZFjPBqkhulxKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604221e4Y08RJN3xPFG7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160422gFMCK1uEcoJ9tUqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160423JtbxMlTsXyeda2wk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160424fLtFClzaQqAcG70T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/3/revitalize-your-ride-with-these-yeezy-air-fresheners\">Yeezy 爱好者可以买的香氛片</a>，英国 Sole Flavours 和 Kick Posters 设计，还有一系列齐全配色（<a href=\"http://www.soleflavours.co.uk/category/air-fresheners\">购买地址</a>）：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160425s9ymPoM1ZLYfdXkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Calvin Klein Collection 2016 春夏黑白海报：<br></p>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160426PlOe9gByG7QXzR2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160427TGaA1CE8SwcV2HUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160428YBotFyKnZLSVPRug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160428WVfriZ4nsDKkOzUS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021604290KiBg2UFh8A6XtVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">韩国化妆品一向以创新、更方便使用为卖点，最近  too cool for school 推出了一款<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/too-cool-for-school-mascara-2/#\">可以调节刷头弯曲角度的睫毛膏</a>，照顾到以往不好刷的死角：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160429UHBk9EGPFNZj0Yt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160430KgSFhbxR7Ujvultr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.165\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}